k. 

Description of Amendment:

 Idaho Power Company (IPC) 
proposes to relocate approximately 0.65 miles of 
transmission lines along Warm Lake Road between State 
Highway 55 and Warm Lake. IPC proposes to relocate the line 
13 to 21 feet due north of the existing line because Valley 
County is widening Warm Lake Road. All new transmission 
poles will be of similar height and configuration to the 
existing poles and will be of raptor-safe design. The 
relocated poles will be within the road right-of-way and 
will meet Valley County's requirement of being no closer 
than 27 feet from the planned centerline of the new road 
alignment. 

