Comment Date: 

May 4, 1994. 

k. 

Description of Proposed Action: 

The existing project, for 
which the exemption is being surrendered, consists of: (1) A 
concrete gravity dam, built in 1920; (2) a power canal with 
an intake gate and a fish passage; (3) a powerhouse with 3 
units having a total generating capacity of 350 kilowatts; 
and (4) appurtenant structures. The project is financially 
infeasible to operate. 

